Technip SA Chief Executive Officer
Thierry Pilenko predicted sustainable and profitable growth in
2011 in an interview with French daily newspaper Le Figaro.  There has been a strong rebound in oil and gas projects,
Pilenko said in the interview.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
